                    \displaystyle \iiint_W {{f}} dV = \int_{ \theta={{theta1}} }^{ \theta={{theta2}} } \int_{r= {{r1}} }^{r= {{r2}} } \int _{ {{w3}}={{h1}} }^{ {{w3}}={{h2}} } {{g}}\ d {{w3}}\ dr\ d\theta={{integ}}.










